Dear Ruprecht, dear Morten,

below you will find two referee reports from Phys.Lett. concerning our
paper on the deuteron. I think we can easily "handle" the suggestions
made by the referee. One of them suggests to add the d/s ratio  calculated
from the various wave functions. We have got the wavefunction in momentum
space. Ruprecht do you know a direct way to calculate this ratio in 
momentum space? 

If you dont have any specific suggestions, I would write a first draft
of a reply, which we would circulate. If you have any good idea, please
let us (Artur and me) know.

Best regards     Herbert

